channel.title: Help with compile
channel.description:
How do i make my sever run people can get in when i have done all port and everything what one should i click compile or runsever ?
if so it compile it says a list of stuff like#
c - Compile your server. r - To Run your server. e - To exit out of the program. jar - It will create your server into an executable Jar archive. color - Change the Text and Backround colors of this compiler. reset - Resets your Compiler Logs.
Option:
what one should i put into the option
